# Habit Forest Support

Welcome to the support page for **Habit Forest**.

If you experience any issues or have questions, please contact us.

## Contact

Email: hbarkine@gmail.com

We usually respond within 1–2 business days.

## Common Questions

### My subscription is not active
Try restoring purchases inside the app.

### I changed devices/deleted the app and lost my progress
Habit Forest currently stores data locally on your device. 
Make sure you enable device backups to prevent data loss.

### The app crashes or behaves unexpectedly
Please restart the app and make sure you are using the latest version available on the App Store.

